=\"https://holland.pk/j2pvb1nz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj2pvb1nz&h=4188c59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日坊間看大和民族常覺得他們團結，民族認同強烈，總會將此情操與源遠流長的歷史掛勾。但歷史上的日本不如今天這樣，近代以前中央政權只能控制首都附近，首都之外各藩的統治能力十分薄弱。而德川政權以前更是一片混亂（即常被電子遊戲挪用的戰國時代），至德川政權雖政治社會皆穩定，但地方仍擁兵自重，有如獨立王國，對中央政權或民族意識認同甚弱。若有個近代以前的日本人回到2017年的今天，聽到松下電器（Panasonic）的社歌︰「為了振興新生的日本，拼命地工作，在充滿笑容的今天，我們士氣高昂地再次集合在一起。」（2015DSEQ3）心想這群日本人定必發了瘋。所謂凡「日本性」，大和是舍萬眾一心的民族，有災難就一同拯救、承擔同貢獻等理念，與其地理情況並不相稱，也不過是代期才出現的產物。</blockquote><br />\n首死人歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eabb98d3688adb332df83ceed2559afe077811","tid":130392,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"quote 你老母呀<br />\n你老母比狗屌<br />\n洗咩板呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"4bf4dac9b042deb271f95a2e05f4778eaeb5394e","tid":130392,"uid":6018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"高質post留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602552112ae995825b655ff69c4de9ca6d03b0a0","tid":130392,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住由邊part講起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大中華膠準備遣唐使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc043b909fac9ea1589c29f367a955655aa3e2bb","tid":130392,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>quote 你老母呀<br />\n你老母比狗屌<br />\n洗咩板呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n嬲嬲豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca60ecf44baf1c195f259e552a5c3397a2a8ccb","tid":130392,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗住由邊part講起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大中華膠準備遣唐使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打算引入完由德川家康講到二十世紀末"},{"pid":"b63dada87c50ffad52114f8b2999f1e2db871203","tid":130392,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/lz3tfxq9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flz3tfxq9&h=3663f802&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n天皇在近代日本歷史中扮演重要的角色，以廿一世紀2017年的角度看來，日本天皇制度可算是世界上碩果僅存的君主政權。但就歷史分析，天皇在19世紀及20世紀權傾朝野，可說是史無前例，或只有公元前7世紀及8世紀時天皇與此相若。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/od0hwn8j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fod0hwn8j&h=1c02db71&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n今日的皇室可追溯至公元4世紀開始崛起的大口家族，時約中國的南北朝，大和家族由擔任皇室氏族男女祭司之職，逐步與相鄰國家爭取霸主地位。到8世紀初，大和族取得政治及宗教權力，並在公元710元在平城（即今日奈良）建立「永久」首都，然至公元794年方在平安（即今日京都）建立真正穩定的政治中心。隨政治社會穩定，大和朝廷下令修史書（《古事記》，有興趣的可以看看），編寫神話譜系，追逐天皇起源至公元前660年，然而修史時已經歷經28個天皇（其中有8個是女性），但都不過是以神話傳統等依據。<br />\n<br />\n隨之後武士集團的興起，日本實行二元政權，天皇也不過是個象徵式的共主（有如今日天皇一樣），至19世紀末先再復活，成為現代版天皇的權力來源。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 日本的正史劃分是以天皇「年號」作標誌，即當新掌權天皇即位，就會冊封年號，情況如中國古代差不多。不過每一朝的年號通常有好幾個，直至近代睦仁天皇（即明治天皇），改元明治（1868），才奠立一舍朝代一個年號的習慣。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ochbkgu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ochbkgu&h=e824775b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>平城京外郭正門羅城門(らじょうもん)模型</strong></div>"},{"pid":"7f5ed55765185cbac58cd1ba66998f935dccbe38","tid":130392,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"那傳統日本到底誰掌實權？答案是武士。所謂武士就是日本的戰士，他們有不同的背景，但都是日後為人所熟悉的人物 &ndash; 明智秀滿、織田信長等名稱相信並不陌生吧（哎想起從前玩過的《信長之野望》）？武士掌權最早可追溯至10世紀（即中國的宋朝），他們原為地方戰士，為貴族和王室服務，後來開始與貴族平起平坐，最後更反客為主，公元1180年鐮倉幕府正好一例。但如上述所指，日本好幾個世紀都在「二元政權」，意即鐮倉幕府雖以武力取得政權，但源賴朝（其領袖）仍請示天皇並要求賜封將軍名號（征夷大將軍），以合法其統治政權。這倒也特別，到底為什麼會發生這樣的事呢？何以日本不能沒有天皇呢？這不是武家們要想的問題，反正東瀛都在他們手上，只要掌握實權一統皇國，留你天皇一個活口又如何。故其之後武家政權，直至近代的德川幕府都由天皇取得將軍名號，以確立其統治合法性。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/459f3hlq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F459f3hlq&h=84f4c3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n源 頼朝(みなもと の よりとも1147-1199)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kxju6b4s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkxju6b4s&h=ecd46d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公武二元政權</div></strong>"},{"pid":"9a1a59823fda5532ac05c61527ac1467ece28cc7","tid":130392,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"支持歷史po"},{"pid":"b41c5de4519c6807a30f04dd0bc4dbd65051aadb","tid":130392,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"一再留名"},{"pid":"479e94a778c40c3dda6e406e11ddecc4a3a9d0ab","tid":130392,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"爛尾啦咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69ebc29747816516e94383040ecc59c62dc1919","tid":130392,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛尾啦咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比啲時間我更新，唔會爛尾放心"},{"pid":"8823caa27015ed7e9054fcef231b3505eaf4c4a3","tid":130392,"uid":6648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cfa15bde23dc19522142d60757cbd917d6116e35","tid":130392,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爛尾啦咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比啲時間我更新，唔會爛尾放心</blockquote><br />\n加油呀，推埋post畀啲人氣出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22b78c44af09515cff2c1f9204d84c9ce6fcc36","tid":130392,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00628f581262930e93cdc3f6732ef94f15f6619","tid":130392,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7148798428e00873649a73b0c1908c5a22953f","tid":130392,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T20:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc39bc4e2e7cd0919a6537e2de4bf0fbec3785d","tid":130392,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T22:16:59.000Z","msg":"lm support"},{"pid":"2bbe0022fa6927aa7c8f3b5742f97aa151e71ec8","tid":130392,"uid":6018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"潛左水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07384b5a4abe402edbe05219cd0d7df0d18f40d","tid":130392,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"等你噢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}